{"type": "article", "id": 7184, "title": "Ora Teapot 茶壶", "description": "", "date": "2015-03-09T07:36:03Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 17, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605234109IRu8JxH1cdWeQoBs.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t传统的茶壶大多又矮又胖，其形状常给存储和放置带来一定的麻烦。Paul Loebach 推出的这一款茶壶试图解决这个问题。这款茶壶长得活像一个实验室里面拿出来的烧杯——没错儿，这个形状的灵感来源也是实验室，不过它看上去比烧杯漂亮多了。你可能还注意到了，这个茶壶没有把手，不过，Paul Loebach 采用双层玻璃的设计也绝对不会让人烫到手呢。<a href=\"http://www.kikkerland.com/products/ora-teapot/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以购买。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234107RZqyfIDkAodQ7tcK.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:696px;\" data-ratio=\"0.61296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234107Y0gU5Hhu1kbVrKTy.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:696px;\" data-ratio=\"0.60462963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234108UYlCoj1c6rVdzBLu.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:696px;\" data-ratio=\"0.61944444\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234108zLsYpOrGBkb8JXd4.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:696px;\" data-ratio=\"0.71203704\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}